"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-rugby-blitzboks-ireland-sevens-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbRugby  ByJacques van der Westhuyzen  Head of Sport  3 minute read  22 July 2024  04:22 pm  The Blitzboks are in action at the Paris Olympics from Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Blitzboks/X  While most of the athletes still have a few days to familiarise themselves with the Olympic Village and what is to come at the 2024 Games in Paris, starting on Friday, that is not the case for the South African Sevens rugby team.\", \"from\": 168, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999984336227, \"rank\": 1.5632616805023582e-09, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 331, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999988617674, \"rank\": 1.138229362088976e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the Blitzboks it's go, go, gofrom tomorrow (Wednesday) when the Sevens tournament gets under way at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tournament is being held at the very start of the Paris Olympic Games and both the men's and women's teams will be in action.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the men, who have been among the world's leading teams over the years, it's a chance to do something special after performing poorly during the most recent World Rugby Sevens Series.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Blitzboks failed to qualify directly for the Games and also missed out through African qualifying.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Only in the last month, following their win at theOlympic repechage tournament in Monaco, did the team of Philip Snyman book their place at the Games.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\", \"score\": 0.8666483440609429, \"rank\": 0.15387046350512765, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\"}, {\"begin\": 1075, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philip Snyman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will now look tomake the most of their good fortuneand try bag a first medal for South Africa.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.1887674621185022e-12, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time the Blitzboks won anything at the Olympics was in 2016 when they came home with bronze from Rio.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1239, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Blitzboks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999953722040336, \"rank\": 4.627817320162539e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it will not be easy for the Blitzboks; they are in a tough pool with Ireland, New Zealand and Japan.\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Blitzboks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999960437, \"rank\": 2.108768113480885e-11, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999570113696, \"rank\": 4.1838485405781383e-08, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1431, \"end\": 1436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999916896594798, \"rank\": 6.856245614723216e-06, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their only focus now though is on the Irish, who have been something of a revelation on the world circuit in the last few years and got the better of the Boks on more than one occasion recently.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9977213651785481, \"rank\": 0.0019242322951680286, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Veteran Rosko Specman, one of the team members of the bronze-winning team from the 2016 Games, is hopeful though the Blitzboks can pull off a surprise first up.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"score\": 0.9999999955432486, \"rank\": 3.5524174735158192e-09, \"text\": \"Rosko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\"}, {\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have given us a hard time this season, but we have seen what they will bring (to the contest),\\\" said Specman ahead of the clash.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This team of ours is ready.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a nice energy and the coach has a good plan for us \\u2026 I think we will have the upphand this time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Blitzboks' opener against Ireland is at 5.30pm on Wednesday, and that's followed by another big clash, against New Zealand at 9.30pm.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2100, \"end\": 2107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999960437, \"rank\": 2.108768113480885e-11, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999570113696, \"rank\": 4.1838485405781383e-08, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their final pool match against Japan is on Thursday at 4pm.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2239, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999916896594798, \"rank\": 6.856245614723216e-06, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's tournament starts on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Blitzboks fixtures and squad  Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2382, \"end\": 2388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9981481456846335, \"rank\": 0.001837719250135986, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2458, \"end\": 2469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Download our app  Get the latest news and updates on Whatsapp  The latest news directly in your inbox  Support Local Journalism  2026 The Citizen.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2541, \"end\": 2549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Whatsapp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2655, \"entities\": []}]}"